"title": "8149: revival, nature of",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "8149",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Scripture indicates that a number of characteristics precede revival, including repentance, humility and obedience.</p>\n<h2>Characteristics which precede revival</h2>\n<h3>God's people long for renewal of their lives</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps80:18\">PSA 80:18</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps74:22\">PSA 74:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps80:1-Ps80:17\">PSA 80:1–80:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps80:19\">PSA 80:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps85:6\">PSA 85:6</a></p>\n<h3>God's people must repent</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr7:14\">2CH 7:14</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs8:46-1Kgs8:50\">1KI 8:46–8:50</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr6:26-2Chr6:27\">2CH 6:26–6:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa64:1-Isa64:7\">ISA 64:1–64:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos5:15\">HOS 5:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts3:19\">ACT 3:19</a></p>\n<h3>God's people experience a new awareness of sin</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs22:11\">2KI 22:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps32:3-Ps32:5\">PSA 32:3–32:5</a></p>\n<h3>God's people need to be humble</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa57:15\">ISA 57:15</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps149:4\">PSA 149:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa66:2\">ISA 66:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic6:6-Mic6:8\">MIC 6:6–6:8</a></p>\n<h3>God's people are revived through God's initiative</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa59:16\">ISA 59:16</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer24:7\">JER 24:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer33:6-Jer33:9\">JER 33:6–33:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Titus3:5\">TIT 3:5</a></p>\n<h2>Characteristic results of revival</h2>\n<h3>People experience inward change</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb8:10-Heb8:12\">HEB 8:10–8:12</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer31:33-Jer31:34\">JER 31:33–31:34</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek11:19\">EZK 11:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts2:42-Acts2:47\">ACT 2:42–2:47</a></p>\n<h3>People live obedient lives</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek11:20\">EZK 11:20</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph4:1-Eph4:3\">EPH 4:1–4:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess1:7-1Thess1:8\">1TH 1:7–1:8</a></p>\n<h3>People are zealous for God's work</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezra5:1-Ezra5:2\">EZR 5:1–5:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hag1:12-Hag1:15\">HAG 1:12–1:15</a></p>\n<h3>People are generous in giving</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod36:5\">EXO 36:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr29:6-1Chr29:9\">1CH 29:6–29:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr31:3-2Chr31:8\">2CH 31:3–31:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts11:28-Acts11:30\">ACT 11:28–11:30</a></p>\n<h3>People delight in worshipping God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezra3:11\">EZR 3:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa12:1-Isa12:6\">ISA 12:1–12:6</a></p>\n<h3>People are joyful</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts13:49-Acts13:52\">ACT 13:49–13:52</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa35:1-Isa35:10\">ISA 35:1–35:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts8:5-Acts8:8\">ACT 8:5–8:8</a></p>",
